# Hourglass AI - Engineering Task Plan

## Current State Analysis
- ✅ Priority 1 (Auth) - Implemented with Firebase Auth, Google Sign-In, Email/Password, session cookies, middleware
- ⬜ Priority 2 (Firestore) - Zustand store only, no Firestore persistence for tasks/goals/results
- ⬜ Priority 3 (Google Calendar) - Not implemented
- ⬜ Priority 4 (Explainable AI) - Basic reasoning exists but no detailed explanations
- ⬜ Priority 5 (Demo Mode) - Still demo-first; landing page directs to demo
- ⬜ New Feature (What is Hourglass) - Not implemented
- ⬜ UI Polish - Needs improvement
- ⬜ Animations - Framer Motion exists but needs intentional usage
- ⬜ Accessibility - Needs improvement
- ⬜ Performance - Needs review
- ⬜ Code Quality - Some dead code (demo-data.ts, demo-selector.tsx)